      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone seeking reliable transportation. The engine and transmission are in solid working order, having received regular maintenance to ensure consistent performance on the road. While the car shows some expected signs of age\u2014including minor cosmetic blemishes on the exterior and visible wear on the interior upholstery\u2014it remains structurally sound and mechanically functional. It is a practical choice for a daily driver that prioritizes utility and reliability over a perfect aesthetic.",
